<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人往灵山上走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山坡上长满了松树、竹子和花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鸟儿们在唱歌，小动物们从他们身边跑过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧停下来，转身看着他的徒弟们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想谢谢你们三个。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们帮我到达了西天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们无数次从妖怪那里救出了我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果没有你们，我是无法到达这里的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。“你不用谢我们，师父。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们都是互相帮助，你帮我变善良了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，我过去做过的坏事，都能被宽恕了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，我打碎天庭琉璃的事情，会被宽恕了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在天庭惹了麻烦，也会被宽恕了。”八戒也说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他朝马挥了挥手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，一定要记得，这匹马，其实是条龙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在自己父亲的宫里放了把火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他也会被宽恕的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看见了吧，师父？我们都非常感谢你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们继续朝山上走，很快就被云遮住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雷音寺上方发出的金光非常耀眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人来到一个大门前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里站着两个门将。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在大门那边，雷音寺的塔和拱门闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们好。”唐僧对门将们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是唐僧，来这里向佛祖取真经的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请进。”一个门将说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧和徒弟们来到一个大房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛祖坐在这个房间的对面尽头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他的佛和菩萨们站在他的身后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨站在佛祖旁边，微笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人低头行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“祝贺你们。”佛祖说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们走了很远的路，经历了很多困难。做得好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空非常激动。他擦了擦眼泪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能来西天取经，我非常荣幸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人们为师徒四人端来了食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人吃完饭后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门将就把他们带到了一个充满光和雾的大房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>木箱成排地摆在墙边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>木箱里有无数的卷轴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太不可思议了。”唐僧嘟囔着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真经都写在这些卷轴上。”门将说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挑出三个卷轴递给唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧看着卷轴，说不出话来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他把卷轴递给了悟净和八戒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把卷轴包好放进了行李里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人再一次在佛祖面前低头行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把真经拿到大唐去吧。”佛祖说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃，又得走很长的路。”八戒嘟囔道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别抱怨了，八戒。”悟空小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒也小声说：“你别对我指手画脚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们俩别吵了。”悟净小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛祖还在说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真经会教那里的人向善、互相帮助。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，真经要好好儿保管。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们非常珍贵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把真经送到大唐后，你们要回到这里领赏。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您别担心，佛祖。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会拼命守护真经的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个门将提议要把师徒四人送到大唐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放心了！”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门将念了一个咒语，他和师徒四人一起从寺院飞了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>345301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛祖回头看了看观音菩萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>345301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧和他的徒弟们做得很好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>350302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>353079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>357851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特别是悟空，在西行中学到了很多东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>357851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>360602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他现在不再那么暴力了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>360602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>364102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我觉得他现在是好的和尚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>364102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>369851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就是这时，一个信使跑进了房间里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>369851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>376526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“观音菩萨！”他喊道，“出问题了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>